# Business Management Platform — Complete Build Guide

We are building a production-grade automated lead, job, finance, and customer management system.
This is an Express + Supabase backend deployed on Railway with an Aura-hosted or custom frontend.

This file contains everything needed to recreate the full system from scratch.
Build it phase by phase in the order listed. Do NOT skip phases.

---

## Tech Stack

- **Runtime**: Node.js with Express 5
- **Database**: Supabase (PostgreSQL + Storage)
- **Hosting**: Railway (auto-deploys on push to main)
- **Email**: Resend API
- **WhatsApp**: Twilio
- **AI Chat**: Anthropic Claude API (Haiku for chat, Sonnet for receipt OCR)
- **Spreadsheets**: Google Sheets API
- **CSV Export**: json2csv
- **Frontend**: Aura-hosted or custom HTML (separate from this repo)

### Dependencies (package.json)

```
@anthropic-ai/sdk ^0.77.0
@supabase/supabase-js ^2.95.3
dotenv ^17.2.4
express ^5.2.1
googleapis ^171.4.0
json2csv ^6.0.0-alpha.2
resend ^6.9.2
twilio ^5.12.1
```

---

## Project Structure

```
/config
  pricing.js              — Default pricing rules (file fallback, overridable via DB)

/middleware
  auth.js                 — Bearer token auth middleware (ADMIN_TOKEN env var)

/routes
  admin.js                — Quote CRUD, pricing settings, attachments, CSV export
  jobs.js                 — Job scheduling, recurring jobs, team members
  customers.js            — Customer profiles, bulk ops, follow-ups, analytics, CSV import
  invoices.js             — Invoice CRUD, email sending, public view
  finance.js              — Expenses, wages, mileage, recurring costs, income, reports, receipt scanning, capital assets, tax savings, audit log
  webhooks.js             — Resend email + Twilio WhatsApp webhook handlers with signature verification

/services
  emailer.js              — All email sending via Resend (6 email types)
  whatsapp.js             — All WhatsApp messaging via Twilio (4 message types)
  chatbot.js              — AI chat assistant via Claude API with tool-based lead capture
  estimator.js            — Rule-based price estimation engine
  scorer.js               — Lead qualification and scoring algorithm
  estimationJob.js        — Async orchestration: estimate + score + notify
  pricingConfig.js        — Pricing config loader with DB override + file fallback + cache
  googleSheets.js         — Quote sync to Google Sheets
  followUpScheduler.js    — Automated 2-step follow-up sequence via node-cron (hourly)

/migrations
  002_add_estimation_and_tracking.sql
  004_add_customer_acceptance.sql
  005_create_customers_table.sql
  006_create_finance_tables.sql
  007_finance_audit_trail.sql
  008_add_follow_up_step.sql
  009_add_deleted_at.sql

/public
  admin.html              — Single-page admin dashboard (8 tabs, dark theme, Tailwind CSS)
  chat-widget.js          — Embeddable chat widget for customer websites
  index.html              — Placeholder landing page
  my-schedule.html        — Team member schedule view
  logo.png                — Business logo

index.js                  — Main Express server, all route registration, quote submission,
                             chat endpoint, acceptance pages
```

