## Database Schema

All tables use UUID primary keys with gen_random_uuid(). All timestamps are TIMESTAMPTZ.
Run migrations in Supabase SQL Editor in numerical order.

### Table: quotes (created manually in Supabase, then extended by migrations)

Core columns:
- id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
- name TEXT NOT NULL
- email TEXT NOT NULL
- phone TEXT NOT NULL
- address_line1 TEXT NOT NULL
- postcode TEXT NOT NULL
- preferred_contact TEXT
- best_time TEXT
- reminders_ok BOOLEAN
- form_version TEXT
- services TEXT[] (array of service slugs, with GIN index)
- answers JSONB (flexible form data)
- status TEXT DEFAULT 'new' (new|contacted|quoted|booked|completed|cancelled)
- source TEXT (form|chat)
- created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()

Added by migration 002 — Estimation & Lead Scoring:
- estimated_value_min NUMERIC(10,2)
- estimated_value_max NUMERIC(10,2)
- lead_score INTEGER (0-100)
- qualification_status TEXT (hot|warm|cold|unqualified)
- conversion_likelihood NUMERIC(3,2) (0.00-1.00)
- estimation_engine_version TEXT
- estimated_at TIMESTAMPTZ

Added by migration 002 — Communication Tracking:
- confirmation_email_sent_at TIMESTAMPTZ
- estimate_email_sent_at TIMESTAMPTZ
- last_contact_at TIMESTAMPTZ
- next_follow_up_at TIMESTAMPTZ
- whatsapp_sent_at TIMESTAMPTZ

Added by migration 002 — Admin Workflow:
- assigned_to TEXT
- admin_notes TEXT
- internal_priority TEXT (high|medium|low)

Added by migration 002 — Conversion Tracking:
- quoted_at TIMESTAMPTZ
- booked_at TIMESTAMPTZ
- completed_at TIMESTAMPTZ
- final_value NUMERIC(10,2)

Added by migration 004 — Customer Acceptance:
- customer_accepted_estimate BOOLEAN DEFAULT false
- customer_accepted_at TIMESTAMPTZ
- customer_response TEXT (accepted|declined|has_questions)

Added by migration 005:
- customer_id UUID REFERENCES customers(id)

Indexes on quotes:
- idx_quotes_qualification_status ON (qualification_status)
- idx_quotes_lead_score ON (lead_score DESC NULLS LAST)
- idx_quotes_conversion_likelihood ON (conversion_likelihood DESC NULLS LAST)
- idx_quotes_next_follow_up ON (next_follow_up_at) WHERE next_follow_up_at IS NOT NULL
- idx_quotes_internal_priority ON (internal_priority) WHERE internal_priority IS NOT NULL
- idx_quotes_quoted_at ON (quoted_at) WHERE quoted_at IS NOT NULL
- idx_quotes_booked_at ON (booked_at) WHERE booked_at IS NOT NULL
- idx_quotes_estimated_value_max ON (estimated_value_max DESC NULLS LAST)
- idx_quotes_customer_accepted ON (customer_accepted_estimate, customer_accepted_at DESC) WHERE customer_accepted_estimate = true
- idx_quotes_customer ON (customer_id)
- GIN index on services array

### Table: customers (migration 005)

- id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
- name TEXT NOT NULL
- email TEXT
- phone TEXT
- address TEXT
- postcode TEXT
- tags TEXT[] DEFAULT '{}'
- admin_notes TEXT
- total_spent NUMERIC(10,2) DEFAULT 0
- total_jobs INTEGER DEFAULT 0
- last_job_date DATE
- first_contact_date TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()
- last_followup_sent_at TIMESTAMPTZ
- created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()
- updated_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()

Indexes: email, phone, postcode, last_job_date
Trigger: auto-update updated_at on modification

### Table: jobs (created manually)

- id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
- quote_id UUID
- customer_id UUID REFERENCES customers(id)
- customer_name TEXT
- customer_phone TEXT
- customer_email TEXT
- address TEXT
- postcode TEXT
- service TEXT
- assigned_to TEXT
- scheduled_date DATE
- time_slot TEXT (morning|afternoon|evening)
- estimated_duration INTEGER
- job_value NUMERIC(10,2)
- status TEXT (pending|in_progress|completed|cancelled)
- payment_status TEXT
- payment_method TEXT
- amount_paid NUMERIC(10,2)
- notes TEXT
- recurring_job_id UUID
- created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()

### Table: recurring_jobs (created manually)

- id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
- customer_id UUID REFERENCES customers(id)
- service TEXT
- frequency TEXT
- next_scheduled_date DATE
- notes TEXT

### Table: team_members (created manually)

- id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
- name TEXT
- phone TEXT
- email TEXT
- notes TEXT
- uuid UUID DEFAULT gen_random_uuid() (public schedule access token)

### Table: invoices (created manually)

- id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
- invoice_number TEXT (INV-0001 format, auto-incremented)
- job_id UUID
- customer_id UUID
- customer_name TEXT
- customer_email TEXT
- customer_phone TEXT
- address TEXT
- postcode TEXT
- service TEXT
- line_items JSONB (array of {description, quantity, unit_price, total})
- subtotal NUMERIC(10,2)
- vat_rate NUMERIC(3,2)
- vat_amount NUMERIC(10,2)
- total NUMERIC(10,2)
- payment_terms TEXT
- due_date DATE
- paid_at TIMESTAMPTZ
- status TEXT DEFAULT 'draft' (draft|sent|paid)
- notes TEXT
- view_token UUID DEFAULT gen_random_uuid() (for public URL access)
- created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()
- updated_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()

### Table: quote_activity (created manually)

- id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
- quote_id UUID
- action_type TEXT (status_change|price_update|priority_change|assignment|note|attachment)
- description TEXT
- created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()

### Table: chat_conversations (created manually)

- id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
- session_id UUID
- ip_address TEXT
- messages JSONB (array of {role, content, timestamp})
- message_count INTEGER
- lead_captured BOOLEAN DEFAULT false
- quote_id UUID
- customer_name TEXT
- customer_email TEXT
- customer_phone TEXT
- customer_postcode TEXT
- first_message_at TIMESTAMPTZ
- last_message_at TIMESTAMPTZ
- updated_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()

### Table: settings (created manually)

- id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
- key TEXT UNIQUE
- value JSONB
- updated_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()

Known keys stored:
- 'pricing_config' — contains SERVICE_PRICING, MODIFIERS, MULTI_SERVICE_DISCOUNT, LEAD_SCORING, QUALIFICATION_THRESHOLDS, CONVERSION_FACTORS

### Table: pricing_history (created manually)

- id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
- changed_section TEXT
- old_value JSONB
- new_value JSONB
- description TEXT
- created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()

### Table: expense_categories (migration 006)

- id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
- name TEXT NOT NULL
- slug TEXT NOT NULL UNIQUE
- colour TEXT DEFAULT '#737373'
- is_tax_deductible BOOLEAN DEFAULT true
- hmrc_category TEXT
- sort_order INTEGER DEFAULT 0
- is_active BOOLEAN DEFAULT true
- created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()

Pre-seed 20 categories: materials, cleaning-solutions, fuel, vehicle-costs, equipment-purchase, equipment-hire, tools, insurance, marketing, subscriptions, uniforms-ppe, phone-internet, training, parking-tolls, bank-charges, accountant, office, licensing, personal, other

### Table: expenses (migration 006)

- id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
- date DATE NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_DATE
- description TEXT NOT NULL
- amount NUMERIC(10,2) NOT NULL
- vat_amount NUMERIC(10,2) DEFAULT 0
- net_amount NUMERIC(10,2) — auto-computed by trigger
- category_id UUID REFERENCES expense_categories(id)
- payment_method TEXT DEFAULT 'bank_transfer'
- is_business BOOLEAN DEFAULT true
- job_id UUID
- supplier TEXT
- reference TEXT
- receipt_path TEXT
- receipt_url TEXT
- recurring_expense_id UUID
- notes TEXT
- created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()
- updated_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()

Indexes: date DESC, category_id, is_business, payment_method
Trigger: auto-compute net_amount = amount - vat_amount on INSERT or UPDATE

### Table: wage_payments (migration 006)

- id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
- team_member_id UUID
- team_member_name TEXT NOT NULL
- date DATE NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_DATE
- amount NUMERIC(10,2) NOT NULL
- payment_type TEXT DEFAULT 'weekly_wage'
- payment_method TEXT DEFAULT 'bank_transfer'
- job_id UUID
- period_start DATE
- period_end DATE
- notes TEXT
- created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()
- updated_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()

Indexes: team_member_id, date DESC

### Table: mileage_log (migration 006)

- id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
- date DATE NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_DATE
- from_location TEXT NOT NULL
- to_location TEXT NOT NULL
- miles NUMERIC(6,1) NOT NULL
- purpose TEXT
- job_id UUID
- rate_per_mile NUMERIC(4,2) DEFAULT 0.45
- is_return BOOLEAN DEFAULT false
- calculated_amount NUMERIC(10,2) — auto-computed by trigger
- notes TEXT
- created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()

Index: date DESC
Trigger: auto-compute calculated_amount = miles * rate_per_mile * (2 if is_return, else 1)

### Table: recurring_expenses (migration 006)

- id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
- description TEXT NOT NULL
- amount NUMERIC(10,2) NOT NULL
- vat_amount NUMERIC(10,2) DEFAULT 0
- category_id UUID REFERENCES expense_categories(id)
- payment_method TEXT DEFAULT 'bank_transfer'
- is_business BOOLEAN DEFAULT true
- supplier TEXT
- frequency TEXT NOT NULL
- day_of_month INTEGER
- next_due_date DATE NOT NULL
- start_date DATE NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_DATE
- end_date DATE
- is_active BOOLEAN DEFAULT true
- last_generated_date DATE
- notes TEXT
- created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()
- updated_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()

### Table: income_entries (migration 006)

- id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
- date DATE NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_DATE
- description TEXT NOT NULL
- amount NUMERIC(10,2) NOT NULL
- source TEXT DEFAULT 'cash_job'
- invoice_id UUID
- job_id UUID
- payment_method TEXT DEFAULT 'cash'
- notes TEXT
- created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()

Index: date DESC

### Table: finance_audit_log (migration 007)

- id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
- table_name TEXT NOT NULL
- record_id UUID NOT NULL
- action TEXT NOT NULL CHECK (action IN ('create', 'update', 'delete', 'restore'))
- changed_fields JSONB
- old_values JSONB
- new_values JSONB
- created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()

Indexes: table_name, record_id, created_at DESC, action

### Table: capital_assets (migration 007)

- id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
- description TEXT NOT NULL
- purchase_date DATE NOT NULL
- purchase_price NUMERIC(10,2) NOT NULL
- category TEXT DEFAULT 'plant_machinery' CHECK (category IN ('plant_machinery', 'vehicle', 'office_equipment', 'tools'))
- aia_claimed BOOLEAN DEFAULT true
- disposal_date DATE
- disposal_value NUMERIC(10,2)
- expense_id UUID REFERENCES expenses(id)
- notes TEXT
- created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()
- deleted_at TIMESTAMPTZ

Indexes: purchase_date DESC, deleted_at partial

### Table: tax_savings (migration 007)

- id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()
- date DATE NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_DATE
- amount NUMERIC(10,2) NOT NULL
- notes TEXT
- created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()
- deleted_at TIMESTAMPTZ

Index: date DESC

### Additional columns added by later migrations

Added by migration 007 — Soft-delete on finance tables:
- expenses: deleted_at TIMESTAMPTZ, deleted_by TEXT
- wage_payments: deleted_at TIMESTAMPTZ, deleted_by TEXT
- mileage_log: deleted_at TIMESTAMPTZ, deleted_by TEXT
- income_entries: deleted_at TIMESTAMPTZ, deleted_by TEXT
- recurring_expenses: deleted_at TIMESTAMPTZ, deleted_by TEXT
Partial indexes on deleted_at WHERE deleted_at IS NULL for each table.

Added by migration 008 — Follow-up tracking:
- quotes: follow_up_step INTEGER DEFAULT 0 (0=none, 1=step 1 sent, 2=step 2 sent)
Index: idx_quotes_follow_up_step

Added by migration 009 — Quote soft-delete:
- quotes: deleted_at TIMESTAMPTZ
Partial index: idx_quotes_deleted_at WHERE deleted_at IS NULL

### Supabase Storage Buckets

1. **quote-attachments** — Public bucket, 10MB max, for quote file attachments. Path: {quoteId}/{timestamp}-{filename}
2. **expense-receipts** — Public bucket, 10MB max, for receipt images. Path: {timestamp}-{filename}

