## API Routes (75+ endpoints)

### Public Routes (no auth)

```
GET    /health                                  — Health check (returns { status, timestamp })
POST   /api/quote                              — Submit quote form
POST   /api/chat                               — Send chat message (rate limited)
GET    /api/chat/history?sessionId=             — Restore chat history
GET    /accept-estimate/:quoteId                — Public acceptance page (HTML)
POST   /confirm-acceptance/:quoteId             — Process acceptance
GET    /invoice/:token                          — Public invoice view (HTML)
GET    /api/my-schedule/:memberId               — Team member schedule (no auth)
PATCH  /api/my-schedule/:memberId/jobs/:jobId   — Team member updates job
```

Webhooks (signature-verified, no bearer auth):
```
POST   /webhooks/resend                        — Email events (delivered, opened, clicked, bounced)
POST   /webhooks/twilio                        — WhatsApp status (sent, delivered, read, failed)
```

### Admin Routes (all require Authorization: Bearer {ADMIN_TOKEN})

Quote Management:
