## Admin Dashboard (public/admin.html)

Single-page app. No framework, no build step. Vanilla JavaScript.
Dark theme (black/neutral-900 background). Tailwind CSS via CDN. Poppins font.
Brand colour: lime-green (#a3e635 / Tailwind lime-400).

Login: Bearer token input stored in localStorage. Validated against /admin/quotes endpoint.

### 8 Tabs:

1. **QUOTES** — List with filters (status dropdown, service filter, date range). Click row to expand detail panel. Update status (new/contacted/quoted/booked/completed/cancelled), priority, notes. Activity log timeline. File attachments (upload/view/delete via Supabase Storage). Customer acceptance tracking. WhatsApp/email links.

2. **SCHEDULE** — Calendar job view by week. Create/edit jobs with customer, service, date, time slot, team member. Drag-style reschedule with email+WhatsApp notification. Availability heatmap (jobs per day for 6 weeks). Generate jobs from recurring patterns.

3. **TEAM** — Team member list (name, phone, email). Add/edit/deactivate. Each member gets a UUID for public schedule access (/api/my-schedule/:uuid).

4. **CUSTOMERS** — Customer profiles with tags (array). Search by name/email/phone. Bulk follow-up campaigns with audience filters (accepted_no_job, quoted_no_response, never_quoted, inactive 3/6/12 months). CSV import (max 1000, duplicate detection by email/phone). Conversion analytics. Per-customer quote + job history. Stats cards (total customers, active, revenue, avg spend).

5. **INVOICES** — Create from completed jobs (auto-populates line items). Edit line items, set VAT rate (0%, 5%, 20%). Send via email with payment details. Public view URL (/invoice/:token). Mark as paid with date. INV-0001 auto-numbering.

6. **FINANCE** — 10 sub-tabs:
   - **Overview**: Summary cards with quick action buttons.
   - **Expenses**: Full CRUD with category dropdown, date, supplier, amount, VAT, payment method (cash/card/bank_transfer), business/personal flag. Receipt paperclip icon linking to stored image. Soft-delete with audit trail.
   - **Receipt Scanner**: Upload receipt photo(s), Claude Sonnet AI extracts date/amount/VAT/supplier. Per-item category splitting for mixed receipts (e.g. fuel + snacks on one receipt become separate expenses). Bulk upload: multi-file select, sequential processing with progress bar, inline-editable review queue, "Save All" creates all expenses.
   - **Wages**: Team member payments with payment type, method, period dates. Soft-delete with audit trail.
   - **Mileage**: From/to/miles with auto-calculation at HMRC rate (0.45/mile). Return trip doubling. Soft-delete with audit trail.
   - **Recurring**: Subscription/regular expenses with frequency, auto-generation.
   - **Income**: Manual income entries (cash jobs, other sources).
   - **Reports**: Summary (P&L with income - expenses - wages - mileage), Cashflow (month-by-month), Category Breakdown (pie chart data), Tax Summary (deductible vs personal, VAT totals, HMRC categories), CSV Export.
   - **Assets**: Capital asset tracking (plant/machinery, vehicles, office equipment, tools). AIA (Annual Investment Allowance) claims. Disposal tracking.
   - **Tax Planning**: Tax forecast with income/expenses/allowances. Tax set-aside tracker for saving towards tax bills.
   - **Audit Log**: Full change history for all finance tables. Filter by table, action type, date range. Shows before/after values for every change.

7. **CHATS** — View all AI chat conversations. See message history. Filter by lead captured. Link to created quote if lead was captured.

8. **SETTINGS** — Pricing configuration editor: service prices by size, modifiers, lead scoring weights, qualification thresholds, conversion factors. Test estimate with mock data. Pricing change history log. Reset to file defaults button.

